INSPIRATIONS & CREDITS:

This project drew inspiration from the following open-source projects:

- Ayije_CDM
  The primary reference for WoW 12.0 CooldownViewer hooking patterns,
  secret value handling, and container management.

- WeakAuras2 (https://github.com/WeakAuras/WeakAuras2)
  License: GNU GPL v2
  The gold standard for WoW combat display frameworks.

- SenseiClassResourceBar (https://github.com/Snsei987/SenseiClassResourceBar)
  License: MIT
  A clean, modern resource bar addon for WoW 12.0.

- Arc UI (https://github.com/devdeadviz/arc-ui)
  A styling framework whose component-based design approach inspired
  the modular UI structure.
